'''热带风暴诺曼'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Norman}}）是2012年9月在[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]西部引发轻度洪灾，同时在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]部分地区产生创纪录雨量的一场热带风暴，也是[[2012年太平洋飓风季|2012年太平洋飓风季]]形成的第14个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]和第14个获命名的风暴，于9月28日清晨在[[下加利福尼亚州|下加利福尼亚州]]最南端附近海域成型。并在当天达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度。气旋北上进入[[加利福尼亚湾|加利福尼亚湾]]，并且当晚就因西南向[[风切变|风切变]]和陆地的影响开始减弱。风暴蜿蜒朝西北方向前进，于9月29日清晨弱化成热带低气压。诺曼此时一度从[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]][[托波洛班波|托波洛班波]]附近登陆，但很快就回到加利福尼亚湾上空。9月29日晚，气旋退化成残留[[低气压|低气压区]]。

面对风暴威胁，气象机构向墨西哥太平洋沿岸部分地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]。墨西哥[[墨西哥行政区划|多个州]]分别进入橙色、蓝色、绿色和蓝色预警状态。该国共开设约553个避难所，但前去躲避的仅有65人。诺曼在[[科利马州|科利马州]]、[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]、[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]、锡那罗亚州、[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]]、[[杜兰戈州|杜兰戈州]]和[[萨卡特卡斯州|萨卡特卡斯州]]降下暴雨，南下加利福尼亚州发生[[泥石流|泥石流]]和洪灾，导致许多道路无法通行，并以[[拉巴斯|拉巴斯]]情况严重。锡那罗亚州多条街道被洪水淹没，约150户家庭被迫离开家园，当地还有约24辆汽车被水卷走。风暴残留在德克萨斯州部分地区产生的降雨量创下新纪录，该州发生洪灾，[[海斯县_(德克萨斯州)|海斯县]][[温布利_(德克萨斯州)|温布利]]有部分道路被淹。另外，还有一名女性因车在路上被洪水卷走而遇难。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Norman 2012 track.png}}
9月12日，一股[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西岸进入大西洋，在向西穿越大西洋盆地期间没有发展出显著的[[对流|深层对流]]。9月23日，东风波已抵达东太平洋，其中的降水和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动在接下来几天里开始增长。9月25日行进至[[阿卡普尔科|阿卡普尔科]]附近海域时，系统再度出现对流爆发，估计这很可能是因为受到[[热带辐合带|热带辐合带]]影响。<ref name="tcr" />[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]在此期间开始针对系统发布热带天气展望<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045125/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201209251732/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201209251732 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | author = Daniel P. Brown | date = 2012-09-25 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201209251732/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201209251732 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，之后每六小时更新一次，指出有发展潜力的扰动天气并预测未来48小时的发展<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnhcprod.shtml#TWO | title = NHC Tropical Cyclone Text Product Descriptions | date = 2013-06-03 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160419044350/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutnhcprod.shtml#TWO | archivedate = 2016-04-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。9月26日，东风波分裂成两部分，其中偏北面的部分朝西北方向逼近墨西哥西南海岸。到了9月27日，系统已组织起足够的深层对流，风速也达到热带风暴强度，只是[[散射仪|散射仪]]所测数据表明其内部还缺少[[大气环流|闭合环流]]。<ref name="tcr" />9月27日发布的热带天气展望预测系统很可能发展成热带气旋<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304203932/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201209272033/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201209272033 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | author = David P. Roberts | date = 2012-09-27 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201209272033/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201209272033 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，但由于系统逐渐逼近陆地，气象部门又在之后的展望中调低对热带气旋形成的预期<ref>{{cite report | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | author = Robbie J. Berg | date = 2012-09-27 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201209272337/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201209272337 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306132929/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/epac/201209272337/index.php?basin=epac&current_issuance=201209272337 }}</ref>。

9月28日，卫星及船只观测数据表明系统内已存在闭合环流<ref name="disc1">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160331134440/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/ep14/ep142012.discus.001.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/ep14/ep142012.discus.001.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Norman Discussion Number 1 | author1 = Michael J. Brennan | author2 = David P. Roberts | date = 2012-09-28 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-31 }}</ref>。[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]早上6点，热带风暴诺曼在[[卡波圣卢卡斯|卡波圣卢卡斯]]（{{lang|en|Cabo San Lucas}}）东南方向约185公里洋面成型<ref name="tcr" />。美国国家飓风中心起初预计风暴会在小幅增强后于9月29日[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，再在次日消散<ref name="disc1" />。但气旋实际上在{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}9月28日中午12点成为热带气旋，接下来继续强化，达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]85公里的最高强度。此后，诺曼开始从西侧的上层低气压区和[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]上空的中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]之间北上。9月28日晚，风暴进入加利福尼亚湾，并因受陆地和[[风切变|风切变]]显著增多的影响而开始减弱。<ref name="tcr" />气旋云层格局在此期间略趋混乱，对流也逐渐同环流分离<ref name="disc2">{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-04-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160404205455/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/ep14/ep142012.discus.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/ep14/ep142012.discus.002.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Norman Discussion Number 2 | author1 = Michael J. Brennan | author2 = David P. Roberts | date = 2012-09-28 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | location = Miami, Florida | deadurl = no }}</ref>。9月29日清晨，诺曼蜿蜒朝西北前进，其环流中心已难以定位，组织结构也变得非常混乱，因此降级成热带低气压<ref name="disc3">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/ep14/ep142012.discus.003.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Norman Discussion Number 3 | author1 = Robbie J. Berg | author2 = Lixion A. Avila | date = 2012-09-29 | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160328072344/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2012/ep14/ep142012.discus.003.shtml | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-03-28 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月29日早上5点，气旋以持续风速每小时55公里强度从[[锡那罗亚州|锡那罗亚州]]托波洛班波（{{lang|en|Topolobampo}}）附近登陆，但很快就又回转朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向移动，再度返回加利福尼亚湾。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月29日中午12点，诺曼退化成残留[[低气压|低气压区]]，这片低气压区缓慢朝西南偏西方向前进，最终于9月30日在[[南下加利福尼亚州|南下加利福尼亚州]][[洛雷托|洛雷托]]附近上空逐渐消散。<ref name="tcr" />

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Norman_Remnants_30_Sep_2012.jpg|thumb]]

{{lang|en|UTC}}9月28日下午15点，[[墨西哥政府|墨西哥政府]]向锡那罗亚州拉克鲁斯（{{lang|en|La Cruz}}）到[[索诺拉州|索诺拉州]][[瓦塔万波|瓦塔万波]]（{{lang|en|Huatabampo}}）之间的太平洋沿岸地区发布[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]，再于次日清晨取消<ref name="tcr" />。锡那罗亚州部分地区进入橙色警报（高风险）状态，南下加利福尼亚州接到黄色警报，索诺拉州南部收到绿色警报，索诺拉州中北部、[[杜兰戈州|杜兰戈州]]、[[奇瓦瓦州|奇瓦瓦州]]和[[萨卡特卡斯州|萨卡特卡斯州]]则接获最低风险级别的蓝色预警信号<ref name="MX1">{{cite news | title = Tormenta tropical "Norman" se forma frente a costas de México | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | url = http://www.prensalibre.com/internacional/Tormenta-tropical-Norman-costas-Mexico_0_782321936.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012053217/http://www.prensalibre.com/internacional/Tormenta-tropical-Norman-costas-Mexico_0_782321936.html | newspaper = Prensalibre | date = 2012-09-28 | location = Mexico City, Mexico | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-10-12 }}</ref>。政府出动400名军人赶赴[[拉巴斯|拉巴斯]]和[[洛斯卡沃斯|洛斯卡沃斯]]，据该州民防部门负责人卡洛斯·恩里克斯·吕康（{{lang|en|Carlos Enriquez Rincon}}）所述，州内有500所学校可以充当临时避难所，足以容纳约三万人，但风暴来袭当晚前往避难所躲避的仅有65人。此外，有关部门还为当地居民送去共计5000个食品包裹。<ref name="MX2">{{cite news | title = Activan Plan DN3 en BCS por tormenta Norman | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873361.html | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-28 | location = Mexico City, Mexico | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073442/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873361.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>墨西哥本土方面，[[库利亚坎|库利亚坎]]当局开设53个避难所，足以容纳7000余人<ref name="MX3">{{cite news | title = Norman se degrada a depresión tropical | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873488.html | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012041218/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873488.html | author = EFE | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-28 | location = Mexico City, Mexico | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，全墨西哥共有五个州的学校停课<ref name="MX4">{{cite news | title = Alertan peligrosidad de tormenta tropical Norman | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873351.html | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | author = Gladys Rodrígue | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305134202/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873351.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-28 | location = La Paz, Baja California Sur | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

热带风暴诺曼在[[科利马州|科利马州]]、[[哈利斯科州|哈利斯科州]]、[[纳亚里特州|纳亚里特州]]、锡那罗亚州、南下加利福尼亚州、杜兰戈州和萨卡特卡斯州产生极端降水<ref name="tcr" />。卡波圣卢卡斯和[[圣荷西卡波|圣荷西卡波]]（{{lang|en|San Jose del Cabo}}）两座港口都禁止船只进出和各种水上活动，其中卡波圣卢卡斯所测浪高达4.6至6.1米<ref name="MX6">{{cite news | title = Tormenta tropical Norman: a 100 km. de Los Cabos | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | newspaper = noticabos.org | author = Giusttav | date = 2012-09-28 | url = https://noticabos.org/2012/09/28/tormenta-tropical-norman-a-100-km-de-los-cabos/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305080344/http://noticabos.org/2012/09/28/tormenta-tropical-norman-a-100-km-de-los-cabos/ | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。拉巴斯有至少24辆汽车被[[泥石流|泥石流]]或洪水卷走<ref name="MX7">{{cite news | title = Colonias en BCS, incomunicadas por Norman | location = La Paz, Baja California Sur | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873466.html | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012041847/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873466.html | author = Gladys Rodríguez Navarro | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-28 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="MX9">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160118140340/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873496.html | title = Sinaloa: desalojan a 150 familias por "Norman" | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873496.html | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-29 | archivedate = 2016-01-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过，气旋在锡那罗亚州产生的雨水还不足以令全州十一座水库水位大幅上涨，平均蓄水量仅从42.5%上升到42.6%<ref name="MX21">{{cite news | title = "Norman" deja de ser una amenaza: SMN | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-30 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/87977.html | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305071605/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/estados/87977.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[马萨特兰|马萨特兰]]附近一艘船只倾覆，船上八名渔民获救<ref name="MX1" />。起初有五位渔民被报失踪，但都在风暴过去后生还<ref name="MX10">{{cite news | title = Se extravian 5 pescadores tras paso de Norman | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873546.html | author = Javier Cabrera Martinez | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305200512/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873546.html | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-29 | location = Culiacán, Sinola | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="MX20">{{cite news | title = "Norman" deja de ser una amenaza: SMN | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873605.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012020643/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873605.html | author = Correspondents | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-30 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，当地还有部分街道被淹<ref name="MX11">{{cite news | title = Tormenta Norman causa inundaciones en Mazatlán | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305073747/http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873376.html | deadurl = no | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/873376.html | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | author = Yovana Gaxiola | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-09-28 | location = Mazatlán, Sinola | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。墨西哥本土沿海地区的两个渔村共有150户家庭疏散<ref name="MX9" />。气旋过后，洛斯卡沃斯、安戈斯图拉（{{lang|en|Angostura}}）和[[纳沃拉托_(锡那罗亚州)|纳沃拉托]]宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref name="MX8">{{cite news | title = Segob declara emergencia en BCS y Sinaloa | url = http://archivo.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/876053.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012051851/http://www.eluniversal.com.mx/notas/876053.html | accessdate = 2013-10-12 | newspaper = El Universal | date = 2012-10-11 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

诺曼的残留在德克萨斯州部分地区产生的降雨量创下新纪录<ref name="US1">{{cite news | author = Todd Hill | title = Under the Weather: Should we worry about Norman? | accessdate = 2014-12-08 | newspaper = Mansfield News Journal | url = http://www.mansfieldnewsjournal.com/article/20121001/NEWS01/121001001/Under-Weather-Should-we-worry-about-Norman-?odyssey=tab | date = 2012-10-01 | archivedate = 2014-12-08 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141208162426/http://www.mansfieldnewsjournal.com/article/20121001/NEWS01/121001001/Under-Weather-Should-we-worry-about-Norman-?odyssey=tab }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | deadurl = yes | url = https://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=2245 | title = Jelawat hits Okinawa; TS Norman feeds heavy rains in Texas | author = Jeff Masters | date = 2012-09-29 | publisher = Weather Underground | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905125347/http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=2245 | archivedate = 2015-09-05 }}</ref>。[[札瓦拉县_(得克萨斯州)|札瓦拉县]]的[[拉普赖尔_(德克萨斯州)|拉普赖尔]]（{{lang|en|La Pryor}}）降雨总量达210毫米，比其他任何地点都高。[[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]][[马布里营|马布里营]]（{{lang|en|Camp Mabry}}）的24小时降雨量达到35毫米，打破1985年所创的日降雨量纪录。不过，德克萨斯州中部大范围地区的降雨量低于预期。[[海斯县_(德克萨斯州)|海斯县]]温布利（{{lang|en|Wimberley}}）有部分道路因洪水临时封闭。<ref name="US3">{{cite news | author = Steven Kreytak | title = Saturday brings less rain than expected to Central Texas | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | newspaper = American-Statesman Staff | url = http://www.statesman.com/news/news/local/saturday-brings-less-rain-than-expected-to-central/nSP88/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141208154427/http://www.statesman.com/news/news/local/saturday-brings-less-rain-than-expected-to-central/nSP88/ | date = 2012-09-30 | archivedate = 2014-12-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>[[纳科多奇斯县_(得克萨斯州)|纳科多奇斯县]]有一辆汽车在路上被洪水卷走，车上一名女性因此丧生<ref name="US2">{{cite news | last = Brett Collar | title = Nacogdoches Co. woman dies during early morning flood | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055553/http://www.ktre.com/story/19678504/etx-woman-dies-during-early-morning-flood | url = http://www.ktre.com/story/19678504/etx-woman-dies-during-early-morning-flood | accessdate = 2016-06-22 | newspaper = KTRE | date = 2012-09-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，[[科珀斯克里斯蒂_(得克萨斯州)|科珀斯克里斯蒂]]区域还收到[[龙卷风警告|龙卷风警告]]<ref name="US3" />。

